Valenwood

Bosmer

Illustration of a Bosmer male

Summary:

  • Homeland of the Wood Elves/Bosmer.

  • Makes up the southwest of Tamriel.

  • A densely forested, sub-tropical region, it is dubbed Tamriel's garden.

  • Valenwood is part of the Aldmeri Dominion.

  • Borders Cyrodiil to the north, and Elsweyr to the east.

Real-world counterpart/inspiration:

Originally just the stereotypical Tolkien/D&D Wood Elves, the closest real-world inspiration would be Native American sprinkled with a bit of Celtic (Iroquois).
